title: Ethiopian Spiced Vegetable Stew
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground turmeric', '1/2 teaspoon ground black pepper', '1 teaspoon ground cloves', '1 teaspoon fenugreek seeds', '1 head garlic, finely chopped', '1 teaspoon salt', '3 large onions, chopped', '4 large carrots, cubed', '4 large potatoes, cubed', '1/4 head cabbage, chopped', '500g tomato puree', '475ml water', 'salt and pepper to taste']
